Will Steinhoff rebound in 2018? Will Naspers have another bumper year? Or will it be a penny stock that heads the list of top performers? Every year Moneyweb invites its community members to pick the stock that they believe will deliver the best return between January and December. Anyone can enter and compete against market commentators and Moneyweb staff to be the annual stock-picking champion. Randall Williams was the winner of the 2017 competition, having picked financial services business Ecsponent. The share gained 176.92% over the period. To enter the competition for 2018, please complete the form below. Entries close on January 20 2018.